should be any day now.

00:11.794 --> 00:14.536
So you're up for a job
at Zephra, huh?

00:14.579 --> 00:15.841
What?

00:15.885 --> 00:17.756
Close the door.
- Oh.

00:17.800 --> 00:19.628
- How did you hear?

00:19.671 --> 00:21.804
- I have my ways.

00:21.847 --> 00:24.154
Specifically, corporate called
and asked me for a reference.

00:24.198 --> 00:25.416
I mean, I have my ways,

00:25.460 --> 00:27.201
but I didn't need to use them
this time.

00:27.244 --> 00:29.159
- Okay.
Well, what did you tell them?

00:29.203 --> 00:30.160
- The truth.

00:30.204 --> 00:31.553
You're smart, hardworking,

00:31.596 --> 00:33.381
and a lot of fun to be around
in medium quantities.

00:33.424 --> 00:34.730
- Okay.
Yeah.

00:34.773 --> 00:35.861
That could've gone worse.

00:35.905 --> 00:38.212
- So what happens
if you get it?

00:38.255 --> 00:40.649
You and Pretty Boy gonna move
out to Zephra HQ,

00:40.692 --> 00:42.694
