for that California life?

00:42.738 --> 00:44.261
Sucking down avocados,

00:44.305 --> 00:46.133
Jonah wearing T-shirts
in pools.

00:46.176 --> 00:47.482
- Jonah doesn't even know
about this yet.

00:47.525 --> 00:49.353
It's just the regional round
of interviews,

00:49.397 --> 00:50.876
and it's such a long shot

00:50.920 --> 00:52.878
that it's not worth getting
into a whole conversation

00:52.922 --> 00:54.271
about our future.

00:54.315 --> 00:56.099
- So this'll just be
our little secret then.

00:56.143 --> 00:57.535
