like nothing is happening.

01:13.812 --> 01:16.119
- One performance of a lifetime
coming right up.

01:16.163 --> 01:18.165
- There's no performance
necessary.

01:18.208 --> 01:19.470
- Don't worry.
I got this.

01:19.514 --> 01:20.732
- Just--less is more!

01:20.776 --> 01:22.517
