but corporate said

01:36.835 --> 01:39.186
that anyone who asks
more than three times can't

01:39.229 --> 01:40.796
'cause of pedophile stuff.

01:40.839 --> 01:43.407
- Hate to agree with corporate,
but that policy feels right.

01:43.451 --> 01:45.757
- It's Easter fever
at our place right now.

01:45.801 --> 01:47.498
Jerry's been practicing
his finding skills

01:47.542 --> 01:48.499
for the egg hunt.

01:48.543 --> 01:50.240
He's--he's getting there.

01:50.284 --> 01:52.416
- Being newlyweds
sounds so fun.

01:52.460 --> 01:54.201
