that you can give a child and--

02:17.311 --> 02:18.834
and it makes sense,
'cause you know,

02:18.877 --> 02:21.358
it can be hard to get pregnant
at our age.

02:21.402 --> 02:23.621
- Oh, I think
I'm actually younger than you.

02:23.665 --> 02:25.449
- Oh.
Okay.

02:25.493 --> 02:26.755
