wanna be a mom

14:10.458 --> 14:13.635
and I'm definitely planning
to adopt,

14:13.678 --> 14:16.203
but I wasn't planning to do it
today.

14:16.246 --> 14:18.161
- Oh, no.
Of course not, no.

14:18.205 --> 14:21.599
Adoption isn't that simple.
It can be a long process.

14:21.643 --> 14:22.687
But as a first step,

14:22.731 --> 14:24.124
I was able to work
my connections

14:24.167 --> 14:25.603
with the foster agency,

14:25.647 --> 14:27.954
and they can arrange for Tony
to sleep at your house

14:27.997 --> 14:28.998
starting tonight.

14:29.042 --> 14:30.304
- Oh.

14:32.349 --> 14:33.960
It's good to have connections.

14:34.003 --> 14:35.657
- You know, Glenn,
you can't expect her

14:35.700 --> 14:38.138
to take this kid into her home
without talking to Jerry first,

14:38.181 --> 14:39.487
right, Sandra?

14:39.530 --> 14:42.272
- Yeah, I should really
discuss this with him.

14:42.316 --> 14:45.014
- Oh.
Yeah, absolutely.

14:45.058 --> 14:46.711
Why don't you call him now?

14:46.755 --> 14:47.930
- Oh, now?

14:49.018 --> 14:50.890
Um, okay.

14:55.372 --> 14:57.374
Hi.
It's me.

14:57.418 --> 15:02.162
Glenn wants us to adopt
a 17-year-old and his sharks.

15:02.205 --> 15:05.339
Uh-huh.
Three of them.

15:05.382 --> 15:06.688
Yep, you're right.

15:06.731 --> 15:07.994
I'll tell him.

15:08.037 --> 15:10.126
Thanks.

15:11.780 --> 15:13.956
He's okay with it.

15:14.000 --> 15:16.045
- Are you sure?

15:16.089 --> 15:17.612
'Cause he could have said
anything,

15:17.655 --> 15:19.309
and we wouldn't know.

15:19.353 --> 15:21.355
- Yeah.

15:21.398 --> 15:24.227
- They loved my passion
and my story.

15:24.271 --> 15:26.273
Apparently, I have a story.

15:26.316 --> 15:28.492
And they're--
they're gonna make me an offer.

15:28.536 --> 15:29.667
- That's great.

15:29.711 --> 15:31.582
So what are you gonna tell 'em?

15:31.626 --> 15:35.238
- I mean,
a high-paying corporate job

15:35.282 --> 15:36.674
where I'll never have to say

15:36.718 --> 15:40.026
the words "raccoon carcass"
again?

15:40.069 --> 15:41.679
I think I--

15:41.723 --> 15:44.073
I think I might take it.

15:44.117 --> 15:46.510
- Oh.

15:46.554 --> 15:48.991
- What?
- No, it's just I--

15:50.123 --> 15:52.081
A second ago,
you seemed so annoyed

15:52.125 --> 15:54.605
by being treated
like the token Latina.

15:54.649 --> 15:57.782
- Yeah, no, I mean--

15:57.826 --> 16:00.655
but at least they're thinking
about diversity.

16:00.698 --> 16:02.439
That's a good thing, right?

16:02.483 --> 16:05.225
- Do you even want
to work there?

16:05.268 --> 16:08.315
- Yeah.

16:08.358 --> 16:11.666
They liked my ideas,
and I think I could--

16:11.709 --> 16:13.146
I could make a difference.

16:13.189 --> 16:15.409
- For a billion-dollar
corporation?

16:15.452 --> 16:17.454
- And for the people here.

16:17.498 --> 16:20.153
- Look, I know that that's
what you want to do,

16:20.196 --> 16:23.112
I get that, but--
I mean, come on.

16:23.156 --> 16:24.635
How often does that
really happen?

16:24.679 --> 16:27.638
- So what am I supposed to do,
Jonah?

16:27.682 --> 16:30.380
Just stay the manager here
forever?

16:32.165 --> 16:35.472
I've been here for 17 years.

16:35.516 --> 16:37.126
I don't have a degree.

16:37.170 --> 16:40.173
Or, like, family connections
or, like, any other options.

16:40.216 --> 16:41.739
This is my chance.

16:44.264 --> 16:46.222
Honestly, I don't care
why they're giving me the job.

16:46.266 --> 16:48.268
It's a good job, and...

16:50.139 --> 16:51.575
I'm gonna take it.

16:53.186 --> 16:54.535
- Well, then...

16:57.581 --> 16:59.453
Congratulations.

16:59.496 --> 17:00.671
- Thanks.

17:07.026 --> 17:08.853
- Hey, Mateo,
can I ask you something

17:08.897 --> 17:10.159
and promise not to freak out?

17:10.203 --> 17:12.031
- No.
- Uh-huh.

17:12.074 --> 17:15.164
Okay, so if 500 people
bought tickets to my party,

17:15.208 --> 17:17.036
how many do you think
will actually show up?

17:17.079 --> 17:18.689
Probably, like, 30, right?

17:18.733 --> 17:20.691
- You sold 500 tickets?

17:20.735 --> 17:22.258
- My friend Chloe reposted it,

17:22.302 --> 17:24.913
so it really took off
in the foot fetish community.

17:24.956 --> 17:27.350
- Chey, this is really bad.
- Well, it's all your fault!

17:27.394 --> 17:29.700
