the responsible adult

17:29.744 --> 17:31.659
who talks me out of doing
dumb stuff.

17:31.702 --> 17:33.139
- You said my ideas were lame!

17:33.182 --> 17:36.229
- They were, but mine were,
like, too good.

17:36.272 --> 17:38.100
Maybe it'll be okay though.

17:38.144 --> 17:39.362
Wait, is there a thing

17:39.406 --> 17:42.278
where if you promise something
to someone

17:42.322 --> 17:43.540
