17:43.584 --> 17:45.934
you have to give them
the thing that you said?

17:45.977 --> 17:47.109
- Yes.

17:47.153 --> 17:48.893
- But, like, legally?
- Yes.

17:48.937 --> 17:51.766
- Oh, dang.
I was hoping no.

17:53.768 --> 17:54.899
- Hey.

17:54.943 --> 17:56.292
Did you hear Amy got that job?

17:56.336 --> 17:58.860
She's gonna be making
so much more money than you.

17:58.903 --> 18:00.340
- Yeah, well, she already does.

18:00.383 --> 18:03.082
- Yeah, but now she's really
running up the score.

18:03.125 --> 18:05.954
