in the hotness rankings.

18:09.697 --> 18:11.960
- So you're okay
with Amy leaving?

18:12.003 --> 18:14.093
- Me?
Oh, no, I hate it.

18:14.136 --> 18:15.224
I'm gonna go home
and stress eat

18:15.268 --> 18:16.921
an entire jar of olives.

18:16.965 --> 18:19.707
But this is pretty huge
for her.

18:19.750 --> 18:21.274
- Yeah. Yeah.
It is, yeah.

18:21.317 --> 18:23.841
It's good that you're being
so supportive.

18:23.885 --> 18:26.105
