- Okay, I get it.

18:39.857 --> 18:41.120
- I think about you
holding a hammer

18:41.163 --> 18:42.251
and try not to laugh.

18:42.295 --> 18:45.080
I'm picturing it now.

18:45.124 --> 18:47.778
