19:24.815 --> 19:27.166
- Oh, 100%.

19:27.209 --> 19:30.256
So I found a really great place
for you.

19:30.299 --> 19:32.388
It's, like, 10 minutes away
from Zephra,

19:32.432 --> 19:34.390
