19:48.187 --> 19:51.494
- I'm--I'm getting on board.

19:51.538 --> 19:53.453
You've got a great opportunity
here

19:53.496 --> 19:56.238
and I'm excited for you.

19:56.282 --> 19:58.458
- So you don't think
I'm selling out.

19:58.501 --> 20:00.764
- I think you're right.

20:00.808 --> 20:02.026
